Subject: Re: [T2] Generator has rough spot - fix or replace?



On Fri, 2 Aug 2002, Miles Erickson wrote:

> I've noticed that my bus's generator doesn't spin freely: there's a
> rough spot where something inside is rubbing gently and audibly against
> something else.

The generator has brushes that indeed rub gently against the commutator.
Is this the rubbing you are referring to?

If you remove the brushes and something is still rubbing, then you need to
replace the bearings or perhaps just get a rebuilt generator.

George Lyle

